Playgro Bathtime Animal Bath Toy (Blue) Price: Rs.380

Key Features

  • Non-toxic and Ensures Child Safety

If your little one cries while bathing
column13: Playgro comes with Bathtime Animal Bath Toy to turn those tears to laughter. This Playgro is ideally suitable for both boys and girls for a fun bathing time. If your little one is 3 months and above this Animal Bath Toy is impeccable for them. This Playgro Bathtime Animal Bath Toy has eight soft toys to entertain your child. This Bath Toy is shaped in such a way
column14: it easy for your little one to get a hold on. There can be no better fun for your child than playing with this bath toy in the lather. You don\u2019t have to worry about the quality of this toy
column15: as it is non-toxic and ensures child safety. This Playgro Bathtime is a chance for your child to relax
column16: de-stress and have fun. This is also a time to introduce your little one to a whole new world of sensory experiences
column17:
from the gentle touch of your hands to the soothing feel of warm water on their body.

\n
